ead to the future is also attempted. Whereas the modeling (including technical modeling) of documents has to date largely been limited to the description of output forms and specific content, the foundations are laid here for including documents’ contexts of use in models that are grounded in cultural theory.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aDocuments.  aGeorg Simmel.  aRoger T. Pédauque.  adocument use.1 aBateman, John A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBohn, Cornelia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHartung, Gerald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHartung, Gerald, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPédauque, Roger T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchlupkothen, Frederik, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchlupkothen, Frederik, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSchmidt, Karl-Heinrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmidt, Karl-Heinrich, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSchneider, Ulrich Johannes, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSkare, Roswitha, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022 Englishz978311099375208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultura